LOOPS

Endless:
begin ... again

Run-Conditional:
begin <condition> while ... repeat

End-Conditional:
begin ... <condition> until

Counted Loops (the iteration number can be accessed w/ var 'i')
do ... loop
: foo
  do
    i . cr
  loop ;

Breaking Loops:
(needs an 'unloop' for each nested loop)
do ... unloop exit ... loop
(breaks the innermost loop)
do ... leave ... loop
